    <string id="tor_religion_description.cult_of_khaine" text="{=str_tor_religion_description_cult_of_khaine}The Cult of Khaine is the dominant religion of the Druchii, centered around the worship of the Bloody-Handed God of Murder. It is a faith of blood sacrifice, ruthless ambition, and the pursuit of power through any means. Khaine's temples are filled with the screams of the dying and the fervent prayers of his disciples, particularly the Witch Elves who serve as his handmaidens." />
